snippet.title: SiNKR 2 Trailer
snippet.description:
SiNKR 2 is a minimalist puzzle game evolved from the award winning SiNKR. There is just you, hooks, pucks, and various contraptions you need to finish each level. Sink all the pucks to advance.

A game by Robert C. Wahler

https://store.steampowered.com/app/973220/SiNKR_2/

Additional Design
Louise Wasilewski

Key Art
Stu Phelps

Background Music
Garden Music
Kevin MacLeod
